This is Audio Logger Prealpha-1
===============================

Copyright (c) 2010, 2011 Gareth Andrew Lloyd

Audio Logger is a unix tool for logging audio from ALSA 
device. The feature set is developed for the primary 
use in a radio station.


Build Instructions
------------------

On Unix, Linux, BSD, OSX, and Cygwin:

    ** No build exists as yet, files come as is **


What's New
----------

This is prealpha nothing new yet?!


Documentation
-------------

Hopfully I'll get a wiki together as features are being developed.


Issue/Feature Tracker
---------------------

All bug reports are being done via sourceforge.  Please use 
the issue tracker:

    https://sourceforge.net/tracker/?group_id=506427


